Package: themefurmanu
Type: Package
Title: Custom Furman ggplot theme and color palettes
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
  person("Scott", "Moore", email = "smoore9@furman.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a reusable ggplot2 theme for Furman-branded data visualizations using IBM Plex fonts (with system fallbacks) that are loaded automatically. Also define multiple color palettes using Furman's brand colors (augmented by a few). 
Depends: R (>= 4.2.0)
Imports:
  ggplot2,
  systemfonts,
  grid
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
